{"h323fec1ag2079g4c89ga3f4g39f4f3e901d3": ["The fire - hurry! Get this thing off of me!", "5fcc3167-5a0c-41e7-b44c-d629d34370cb", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_StuckHalfElf.html", "8def607f-cfd3-96cd-94e6-8301ff6e4dbf"], "h1b1134bfgafbeg4f37gb813g79c001c2314a": ["<i>Brace yourself to lift the wreckage.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_StuckHalfElf.html", "cd80074e-804f-b3b3-d5f4-7bc63ae5f23a"], "h2dd44bebgf095g4c52gb2d0gf2a783352a52": ["Almost... there!", "5fcc3167-5a0c-41e7-b44c-d629d34370cb", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_StuckHalfElf.html", "a580f547-24d7-831b-f7cf-871eff506648"], "h362e9561g9bc7g45e2gbaa4gee43d34f4e20": ["Thank you... now how the hell do we get out of here?", "5fcc3167-5a0c-41e7-b44c-d629d34370cb", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_StuckHalfElf.html", "4ee0eee8-ff27-7696-1846-e17ba55765ed"], "h0644053eg53c1g496dg8b8cgd9c1e4746bda": ["The door's that way.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_StuckHalfElf.html", "1da33bb0-afc7-a211-06ae-25b4dd4006a4"], "h61b09c84gba9eg4346gb44bg733959876803": ["The smoke - I can't see a damn thing!", "5fcc3167-5a0c-41e7-b44c-d629d34370cb", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_StuckHalfElf.html", "a4918082-18dc-071d-9d7a-e7d087e03be5"], "h33b66d69g9e36g466fga5e3g94780c7a4af3": ["You're on your own.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_StuckHalfElf.html", "6f4b048e-a6c7-eb9b-4ccf-5105baac7456"], "h41601be1g4a3bg45cegad6dg7e013b3a053f": ["Oh, gods. I'll have to make a run for it.", "5fcc3167-5a0c-41e7-b44c-d629d34370cb", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_StuckHalfElf.html", "c6355874-86ae-a0d8-717a-c49d302b0142"], "h54ed7290gdfc6g4642g89a6g4192f9937ab6": ["Come on, follow me.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_StuckHalfElf.html", "4a78e146-18f8-7aac-cc37-663ace521d5d"], "h75735f0ag606cg4b99ga89ag363b53dbfaa7": ["Right. I'll try to keep up.", "5fcc3167-5a0c-41e7-b44c-d629d34370cb", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_StuckHalfElf.html", "f5b4f681-2d83-b2d0-aa8f-d77e17f02d56"], "h373b6a0egd307g43b9gae31gc85d50457797": ["Thank you, thank you!", "5fcc3167-5a0c-41e7-b44c-d629d34370cb", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_StuckHalfElf.html", "ec9556ef-bfbf-b28e-ac1c-30c35b2a1626"], "h1c8cfbb3gba8fg44d0gac28ga8fdda4a6895": ["Damn... just go. I'm done for.", "5fcc3167-5a0c-41e7-b44c-d629d34370cb", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_StuckHalfElf.html", "711bdc43-aa32-6fb0-0b5c-96f08d4ecd05"], "h28faa038gf9cag4ff8g9e5cgc092ad512798": ["<i>Find leverage to shift the beam.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_StuckHalfElf.html", "94b38e0d-95ce-8cc3-6afa-411c4c1f518b"], "hc2fbe182gfc8fg4f5bg9714g94f6bb11f11e": ["I think... that's it!", "5fcc3167-5a0c-41e7-b44c-d629d34370cb", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_StuckHalfElf.html", "00da991e-17e4-6412-ce8c-48bf979a6cea"], "hbef896d0g2980g4fa7g88e7g6941b8adfeb2": ["Damn... just go. I'm done for.", "5fcc3167-5a0c-41e7-b44c-d629d34370cb", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_StuckHalfElf.html", "27246c36-3918-8570-015e-3c5991691c3e"], "h39358380gb2ccg4843gbb58g45ffa566d19a": ["<i>Leave.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_StuckHalfElf.html", "6a0ca766-add4-0891-44cb-36448f1b5b0c"], "h66b8f7dagc2bdg4da4gad84g1e73e636ae92": ["*Cough!*", "5fcc3167-5a0c-41e7-b44c-d629d34370cb", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_StuckHalfElf.html", "086bdcba-9d99-f684-83e4-be0c2b8c3ca5"]}